-- Deutsche Post to Expand Network in Germany to Better Reach Private Clients
-- Mike Gavin
-- 2010-04-23T08:18:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/deutsche-post-to-expand-network-in-germany-to-better-reach-private-clients.html

          
          
             Deutsche Post AG will
“extensively” expand its network across Germany this year to
increase availability for private customers, the company said in
an e-mailed statement today. The company will add 4,000 points
of sale, 2,000 letter boxes and 150 packstations, it said.  
          
          


  


        